2.10
|
Data and code availability
This study's data is from the ABCD Study. It is available through the
National Institute of Mental Health Data Archive (https://nda.nih.
gov/abcd). Analysis scripts and a corresponding wiki can be found at
https://github.com/VU-BRAINS-lab/Reimann_ADHD_Volume.
